2025-11-21CIRNACOther Than Statutory AuthorityOrder Amending the Yukon First Nation Self-Government AgreementsOrder Amending the Yukon First Nation Self-Government Agreements in order to (1) enable the Government of Yukon and these First Nations to negotiate the division and sharing of responsibility related to delivery, design and administration of education programs delivered in the First Nations’ Traditional Territory; and (2) correct an inadvertent omission related to amendments to the agreement in 2023.N/A
subject: Order Amending the Yukon First Nation Self-Government Agreements
precis: Order Amending the Yukon First Nation Self-Government Agreements in order to (1) enable the Government of Yukon and these First Nations to negotiate the division and sharing of responsibility related to delivery, design and administration of education programs delivered in the First Nations’ Traditional Territory; and (2) correct an inadvertent omission related to amendments to the agreement in 2023.
